data.title: Asya - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Asya: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

TikTok star known for her asyayvn account, which has garnered 310,000 followers. She primarily posts lip-sync videos to popular songs on TikTok. She also posts beauty content including makeup application videos and hairstyle videos. She has featured cosmetic products from brands like Chanel and Flower Knows.

Before Fame

She began posting to her TikTok account in December 2021. She went to fashion school in Milan.

Trivia

She has a popular Instagram account asyayvn, which has amassed 150,000 followers. On her Instagram, she frequently posts photos of herself wearing bright, elegant outfits. In contrast to her choice of outfits, her photos have a very dark and desaturated tone to them.

Family Life

She was born in Germany and later resided in Milan.
